sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as User or RPC client
    participant Main as coding-agent main.ts
    participant Runtime as AgentSessionRuntime
    participant Session as AgentSession
    participant Ext as ExtensionRunner
    participant Agent as Agent
    participant AgentLoop as agent-loop.ts
    participant AI as pi-ai streamSimple
    participant Provider as LLM provider
    participant Tool as Built-in or extension tool
    participant Store as SessionManager JSONL
    participant Mode as TUI print JSON RPC mode

    User->>Main: Start pi with flags input files stdin or RPC
    Main->>Main: Parse args select mode resolve cwd/session/resources/model
    Main->>Runtime: createAgentSessionRuntime(factory, sessionManager)
    Runtime->>Session: createAgentSessionFromServices(...)
    Session->>Ext: bind core APIs and load extension runtime
    Session->>Session: create built-in tools and active system prompt
    Main->>Mode: Run interactive print JSON or RPC mode
    Mode->>Session: prompt(text, images, source, streamingBehavior)
    Session->>Ext: extension command and input handlers
    Ext-->>Session: handled transformed input or continue
    Session->>Session: expand skill/template check model/auth compact if needed
    Session->>Ext: before_agent_start(prompt, images, systemPrompt)
    Ext-->>Session: optional custom messages and system prompt override
    Session->>Agent: prompt(AgentMessage[])
    Agent->>AgentLoop: runAgentLoop(messages, context snapshot, loop config)
    AgentLoop->>Session: emit user message_start/message_end
    Session->>Ext: mirror message lifecycle
    Session->>Mode: forward/render event
    Session->>Store: appendMessage(user)
    AgentLoop->>Ext: context handlers through transformContext
    AgentLoop->>AI: streamSimple(model, context, auth/options)
    AI->>Ext: before_provider_request payload hook
    AI->>Provider: Provider streaming request
    Provider-->>AI: text thinking tool-call events
    AI-->>AgentLoop: assistant stream events and final result
    AgentLoop->>Session: message_update events during streaming
    Session->>Ext: message_update handlers
    Session->>Mode: render or emit updates
    AgentLoop->>Session: assistant message_end
    Session->>Ext: message_end handlers may replace same-role message
    Session->>Store: appendMessage(assistant)
    alt Assistant requested tools
        AgentLoop->>Session: tool_execution_start
        Session->>Ext: tool_execution_start and tool_call hook
        Ext-->>Session: allow or block tool call
        alt Tool allowed
            AgentLoop->>Tool: execute(toolCallId, args, signal, update)
            Tool-->>AgentLoop: result or thrown error
            AgentLoop->>Session: tool_execution_update/end
            Session->>Ext: tool_result hook
            Ext-->>Session: optional result mutation
        else Tool blocked or invalid
            AgentLoop->>AgentLoop: create error tool result
        end
        AgentLoop->>Session: toolResult message_start/message_end
        Session->>Store: appendMessage(toolResult)
        AgentLoop->>AI: Next provider call with tool result context
    end
    AgentLoop->>Agent: agent_end when no tool calls or queued messages remain
    Agent->>Session: awaited event listeners settle and run becomes idle
    Session->>Session: post-run retry compaction or extension-queued continuation
    Session-->>Mode: final response or protocol events
